entries.title: Florida launches child ID program
entries.description: (The Center Square) – Florida has launched a new Child ID program and is distributing Child ID kits to all Florida school districts for parents of kindergarteners, Attorney General Ashley Moody announced.

entries.title: McConnell threatens short-term continuing resolution if Democrats don't meet omnibus demands
entries.description: Senate Minority Leader Mitch McConnell (R-KY) threatened a short-term continuing resolution on Monday if Senate Democrats do not meet his demands for a large spending bill.
